'''泰坦鳥'''（[[學名|學名]]''Titanis''）是一[[屬|屬]]非常大及[[不會飛的鳥|不能飛]]的[[肉食性|肉食性]][[鳥類|鳥類]]，其名字是以[[古希臘|古希臘]]神話[[奧林匹斯十二主神|奧林匹斯十二主神]]之前的神明[[泰坦|泰坦]]來命名，意謂其巨大的身型。泰坦鳥屬下只有一[[種|種]]，稱為「泰坦巨鳥」（''T. walleri''），是紀念[[完模標本|完模標本]]的發現者Benjamin I. Waller。牠生存於490-180萬年前的[[北美洲|北美洲]]，在[[美國|美國]][[科羅拉多州|科羅拉多州]]及[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]都有發現其[[化石|化石]]。估計牠們直至15000年前才[[滅絕|滅絕]]<ref name="baskin1995">{{Cite journal en|author=Baskin, J. A.|year=1995|title=The giant flightless bird ''Titanis walleri'' (Aves: Phorusrhacidae) from the Pleistocene coastal plain of South Texas|journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology|volume=15|issue=4|pages=842-844}}</ref>，但更準確的估計是最少於180萬年前就已經滅絕了。<ref name="mcfaddenetal2006">{{Cite journal en|author=McFadden, B., Labs-Hochstein, J., Hulbert, R.C. Jr., and Baskin, J.A.|year=2006|title=Refined age of the late Neogene terror bird (''Titanis'') from Florida and Texas using rare earth elements|journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology|volume=26|issue=3|pages=92A|url=http://users.tamuk.edu/kfjab02/pdf%20jpg%20gif%20files/Titanis%20SVP.pdf|access-date=2007-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004112214/http://users.tamuk.edu/kfjab02/pdf%20jpg%20gif%20files/Titanis%20SVP.pdf|archive-date=2018-10-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="mcfaddenetal2007">{{Cite journal en|author=McFadden, B., Labs-Hochstein, J., Hulbert, R.C. Jr., and Baskin, J.A.|year=2007|title=Revised age of the late Neogene terror bird (''Titanis'') in North America during the Great American Interchange|journal=Geology|volume=35|issue=2|pages=123-126|doi=10.1130/G23186A.1|url=http://www.gsajournals.org/perlserv/?request=res-loc&uri=urn%3Aap%3Apdf%3Adoi%3A10.1130%2FG23186A.1|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120217041322/http://www.gsajournals.org/perlserv/?request=res-loc&uri=urn:ap:pdf:doi:10.1130%2FG23186A.1|archivedate=2012-02-17}}</ref>泰坦鳥是屬於巨大及不能飛的[[駭鳥|駭鳥]]，在分支中屬較年輕的物種。身高可達 {{convert|2.5|m|ftin|abbr=on}}，體重則約 {{convert|150|kg|lb}}<ref>{{Cite book|title=Living Dinosaurs: The Evolution of Modern Birds|last=Dyke|first=Gareth|publisher=John Wiley and Sons, Inc.|date=15 February 2011|isbn=|location=|pages=}}</ref>。

== 描述 ==
[[File:Skeleton_of_Titanis_at_the_Florida_Museum_of_Natural_History.jpg|thumb]]
泰坦鳥估計約高 {{convert|1.4|to|2.5|m|ftin|abbr=on}} 及重 {{convert|150|kg|lb}}，但差異較大，故牠們有可能是[[兩性異形|兩性異形]]。<ref name="alvarenga&hofling2003">{{Cite journal en|author=Alvarenga, H.M.F., and Höfling, E.|year=2003|title=Systematic revision of the Phorusrhacidae (Aves: Ralliformes)|journal=Papéis Avulsos de Zoologia|volume=43|issue=4|pages=55-91|url=http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?script=sci_pdf&pid=S0031-10492003000400001&lng=en&nrm=iso&tlng=en|access-date=2007-12-24|archive-date=2017-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170520065132/http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?script=sci_pdf&pid=S0031-10492003000400001&lng=en&nrm=iso&tlng=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然未有發現牠的[[頭顱骨|頭顱骨]]，但從其近親可以肯定它是很大，且有像[[斧頭|斧頭]]的鳥嘴。

牠的雙翼細小，故不可能用來飛翔，相反有一對爪可以用來抓住獵物<ref name="chandler1994">{{cite journal|author=Chandler, R.M.|year=1994|title=The wing of ''Titanis walleri'' (Aves: Phorusrhacidae) from the Late Blancan of Florida|journal=Bulletin of the Florida Museum of Natural History, Biological Sciences|volume=36|pages=175–180|url=http://ufdcweb1.uflib.ufl.edu/UF00099062|access-date=2019-02-15|archive-date=2017-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171020084323/http://ufdcweb1.uflib.ufl.edu/UF00099062|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而在之後的研究發現，泰坦鳥的前肢構造與牠們現存的近親[[叫鶴科|叫鶴科]]（泰坦鳥、[[恐鶴|恐鶴]]、叫鶴均屬於[[叫鶴目|叫鶴目]]）十分雷同，但叫鶴的前肢並不具有爪，因此泰坦鳥的前肢可能其實並不具有可以抓握獵物的爪<ref name=gould2005>{{cite journal|author1=Gould, G.C.|author2=Quitmyer, I.R.|lastauthoramp=yes|year=2005|title=''Titanis walleri'': bones of contention|journal=Bulletin of the Florida Museum of Natural History|volume=45|pages=201–229|url=http://www.flmnh.ufl.edu/bulletin/gouldquitmyerlowres.pdf|access-date=2019-02-15|archive-date=2012-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121215170638/http://www.flmnh.ufl.edu/bulletin/gouldquitmyerlowres.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

整體而言，泰坦鳥非常近似牠們在[[南美洲|南美洲]]的近親：[[恐鶴|恐鶴]]及 ''{{link-en|Devincenzia}}''，但擁有較粗短的脖子，以及較為粗壯的身體。就牠的遺骸所知甚少，只知道比 ''Devincenzia'' 的腳窄，但中趾則按比例較大。<ref name="brodkorb1963">{{Cite journal en|author=Brodkorb, P.|year=1963|title=A giant flightless bird from the Pleistocene of Florida|journal=Auk|volume=80|issue=2|pages=111-115|url=http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Auk/v080n02/p0111-p0115.pdf|access-date=2007-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091211132411/http://elibrary.unm.edu/sora/Auk/v080n02/p0111-p0115.pdf|archive-date=2009-12-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 

泰坦鳥為肉食性，但可能多半以當時的小型哺乳動物為食<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://vertpaleo.org/Society-News/SVP-Paleo-News/Society-News,-Press-Releases/Press-Release-Exceptionally-preserved-fossil-gives.aspx|title=Society of Vertebrate Palaeontology|last=Degrange|first=Federico|date=|website=|access-date=|archive-date=2018-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181209213219/http://vertpaleo.org/Society-News/SVP-Paleo-News/Society-News,-Press-Releases/Press-Release-Exceptionally-preserved-fossil-gives.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。


